The paper deals with the problem of spike deconvolution, which is a common problem in image processing and signal analysis. The use of total variation regularization and convex optimization techniques suggests that the paper may belong to the sub-categories of information theory (cs.IT), computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV), numerical analysis (cs.NA), signal processing (cs.SI), or machine learning (cs.LG).
